"damage."
msgstr ""
"Кожне <style=cIsDamage>5-те використання основної здібності</style> випускає "
"примарний снаряд, що завдає <style=cIsDamage>200%</style> "
"<style=cStack>(+200% за кожен дублікат)</style> базової шкоди."

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_SHACKLEDLAMP_LORE
msgid ""
"\"Excuse me.\"\n"
"\n"
"\"Yes, over here, please. I need to ask you something.\"\n"
"\n"
"\"Closer, now.\"\n"
"\n"
"\"I need your help. This lantern you see before you, it is merely a "
"fractured piece of a greater body.\"\n"
"\n"
"\"The journey? Ah, yes. It will be long, but do not fret. I will guide you "
"wherever you must go, and, while it may be fraught with danger, it will be "
"nothing I cannot assist you with.\"\n"
"\n"
"\"Hm? What's in it for you, you say?\"\n"
"\n"
"\"Oh, you will see. Your reward will be far greater than you could possibly "
"imagine. Once I have returned to my full splendor, I will protect you. I "
"will keep you safe. Keep you warm. Make you powerful. All your worries will "
"be burned away. Doesn't that sound wonderful?\"\n"
"\n"
"\"You agree? Good. Now, pick up the lantern, quickly.\"\n"
"\n"
"\"We have a long journey ahead of us, friend.\""
msgstr ""
"«Перепрошую.»\r\n"
"\r\n"
"«Так, сюди, будь ласка. Я хочу вас дещо запитати.»\r\n"
"\r\n"
"«Ближче.»\r\n"
"\r\n"
"«Мені потрібна ваша допомога. Лампа, яку ви бачите, це лиш уламок більшого "
"тіла.»\r\n"
"\r\n"
"«Подорож? А, так. Вона буде довгою, але не хвилюйтесь. Я проведу вас, куди б "
"вам не треба було дістатися. Навіть перед обличчям небезпеки, не буде "
"нічого, з чим я не зможу вам допомогти.»\r\n"
"\r\n"
"«Хм? Що вам з цього, питаєте?»\r\n"
"\r\n"
"«Ох, бачте. Ваша винагорода буде набагато більшою, ніж ви можете собі "
"уявити. Як тільки я поверну собі мою колишню велич, я захищу вас. Триматиму "
"вас у безпеці. Зігріватиму вас. Наділю вас силою. Всі ваші турботи зникнуть. "
"Звучить чудово, хіба ні?»\r\n"
"\r\n"
"«Ви погоджуєтеся? Добре. Тепер, беріть лампу, швидше.»\r\n"
"\r\n"
"«Попереду нас чекає довга дорога, друже.»"

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_STIRRINGSOUL_NAME
msgid "Stirring Soul"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_STIRRINGSOUL_DESC
msgid ""
"Slain monsters leave a <style=cIsUtility>soul</style> which has a "
"<style=cIsUtility>{0}%</style> <style=cStack>(+{0}% per unsuccessful roll, "
"resetting on success)</style> chance to <style=cIsUtility>spawn an item</"
"style> on pickup."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_STIRRINGSOUL_PICKUP
msgid "<link=\"textWavy\">What am I fighting for?</link>"
msgstr "<link=\"textWavy\">Заради чого я борюся?</link>"

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_STIRRINGSOUL_LORE
msgid ""
"A spirit of determination...\n"
"<link=\"textWavy\">...A spirit to be stopped.</link>\n"
"An unwavering will to survive...\n"
"<link=\"textWavy\">...A flickering will to survive.</link>\n"
"\n"
"Willing to desecrate their identity...\n"
"<link=\"textWavy\">...Willing to desecrate their memory.</link>\n"
"Willing to sacrifice their civilization...\n"
"<link=\"textWavy\">...Willing to sacrifice their humanity.</link>\n"
"\n"
"To what lengths will they go to live?\n"
"<link=\"textWavy\">To what lengths will they go to bring themselves ruin?</"
"link>\n"
"To what lengths will they go to escape?\n"
"<link=\"textWavy\">To what lengths will they go to destroy?</link>\n"
"\n"
"All in the name of self preservation...\n"
"<link=\"textWavy\">...All in the name of narcissism.</link>\n"
"All for the sake of an uncertain hope...\n"
"<link=\"textWavy\">...All for the sake of a null chance.</link>\n"
"\n"
"What would happen if given an opportunity?\n"
"<link=\"textWavy\">What would happen if given an ally?</link>\n"
"What would happen if their fire was stoked?\n"
"<link=\"textWavy\">What would happen if they were given false hope?</link>\n"
"\n"
"Maybe they should be given a chance.\n"
"<link=\"textWavy\">Maybe they should be given strength.</link>\n"
"Maybe they should be given an offer.\n"
"<link=\"textWavy\">Maybe they should be taken first.</link>"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_MOXIE_NAME
msgid "<color=#FFCCED>Moxie</color>"
msgstr "<color=#FFCCED>Моксі</color>"

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_MOXIE_DESC
