"style> during <color=#FFCCED>storms</color>."
msgstr ""
"Підвищує <style=cIsUtility>ВСІ характеристики</style> на "
"<style=cIsUtility>50%</style> під час <color=#FFCCED>штормів/бурь тощо</"
"color>."

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_MOXIE_PICKUP
msgid "<color=#FFCCED>How much more?</color>"
msgstr "<color=#FFCCED>Скільки ще?</color>"

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_MOXIE_LORE
msgid ""
"Hey! You! In this file! You probably shouldn't be here... Keep quiet, okay?"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_REMUNERATION_NAME
msgid "Remuneration"
msgstr "Винагорода"

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_REMUNERATION_DESC
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A <style=cIsUtility>choice</style> between three <style=cIsHealth>powerful "
"items</style> appears at the <style=cIsUtility>start of each stage</style>."
msgstr ""
"Поруч з'являється <style=cIsUtility>вибір</style> між трьома "
"<style=cIsHealth>потужними предметами</style> <style=cIsUtility>на початку "
"кожного етапу</style>."

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_REMUNERATION_PICKUP
msgid "<link=\"textWavy\">... At what cost?...</link>"
msgstr "<link=\"textWavy\">... Якою ціною?...</link>"

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_REMUNERATION_FAILURE
msgid "<color=#f4adfa><link=\"textWavy\">How memorable...</link></color>"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_REMUNERATION_TERMINAL_NAME
msgctxt ".strings.SS2_REMUNERATION_TERMINAL_NAME"
msgid "Pedestal"
msgstr "П'єдестал"

#: .strings.SS2_REMUNERATION_TERMINAL_CONTEXT
msgid "<link=\"textWavy\">Complete transaction</link>"
msgstr "<link=\"textWavy\">Завершити транзакцію</link>"

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_REMUNERATION_LORE
msgid ""
"<link=\"textShaky\">What is your legacy?</link>\n"
"\n"
"Nothing but petty vengeance.\n"
"\n"
"<link=\"textShaky\">What is your identity?</link>\n"
"\n"
"Nothing but a name spoken in disgust.\n"
"\n"
"<link=\"textShaky\">What do you want?</link>\n"
"\n"
"Nothing but a new purpose.\n"
"\n"
"<link=\"textShaky\">What do you need?</link>\n"
"\n"
"Nothing but the weapons that I trust.\n"
"\n"
"<link=\"textShaky\">So, where will you go?</link>\n"
"\n"
"Wherever you make me go.\n"
"\n"
"<link=\"textShaky\">Then, what will you do?</link>\n"
"\n"
"Whatever you say you need.\n"
"\n"
"<link=\"textShaky\">Is that all, then?</link>\n"
"\n"
"If you say it so.\n"
"\n"
"<link=\"textShaky\">Then go there, and die.</link>\n"
"\n"
"...\n"
"\n"
"As long as you're paying me."
msgstr ""

