#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFDUALITY_NAME
msgid "Relic of Duality"
msgstr "Реліквія дуальності"

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFDUALITY_DESC
msgid ""
"Damaging enemies burns them for <style=cMono>FIGURE OUT THIS MATH LOL</"
"style> <style=cStack>(+something% per stack)</style>. <style=cDeath>Being "
"hit freezes you for some seconds idfk lol figure out when this item is "
"implemented</style>"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFDUALITY_PICKUP
msgid "All attacks burn enemies. <style=cDeath>All damage freezes you.</style>"
msgstr ""
"Всі атаки підпалюють ворогів. <style=cDeath>Вся шкода заморожує вас.</style>"

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFDUALITY_LORE
msgid ""
"Hmm? Oh, Youngling! You are back sooner than expected. Have you completed "
"your search?\n"
"\n"
"Oh, dear. Youngling, why are you shivering? Has something hurt you?\n"
"\n"
"You found something that hurt you? Hmm. Peculiar. Do you have it with you, "
"still?\n"
"\n"
"...I see. Let me look at it, then. Come now, and show me what you've found.\n"
"\n"
"Hmm. A strange thing, this one. A blazing fire, yet cold to the touch. How "
"unnatural, this is. There's a certain harmony to it, however. As the heat "
"brings warmth and life, the cold tempers it, and keeps it in check. But in "
"that same way, that bitter cold may bring despair and death without the heat "
"to stave it off.\n"
"\n"
"...Oh, but there I go, rambling once more. You need to be taken care of, "
"Youngling. Please, come with me."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFEXTINCTION_NAME
msgid "Relic of Extinction"
msgstr "Реліквія вимирання"

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFEXTINCTION_DESC
msgctxt ".strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFEXTINCTION_DESC"
msgid "WIP DESC"
msgstr "ОПИС В РОЗРОБЦІ"

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFEXTINCTION_PICKUP
msgid ""
"A black hole follows you that deals extreme damage, BUT it can damage you."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFEXTINCTION_LORE
msgctxt ".strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFEXTINCTION_LORE"
msgid "WIP LORE"
msgstr "ЗАПИС В РОЗРОБЦІ"

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFFORCE_NAME
msgid "Relic of Force"
msgstr "Реліквія тяги"

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFFORCE_DESC
msgid ""
"All attacks strike <style=cIsDamage>1</style> <style=cStack>(+1 per stack)</"
"style> additional time for <style=cIsDamage>{1}%</style> TOTAL damage. "
"<style=cIsUtility>Consecutive strikes</style> to the same enemy increase "
"damage dealt by <style=cIsDamage>{1}%</style>, up to a maximum of "
"<style=cIsDamage>{2}%</style> TOTAL damage dealt. <style=cDeath>Reduce "
"attack speed and increase skill cooldowns by {0}%</style> <style=cStack>(-"
"{0}% per stack)</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFFORCE_PICKUP
msgid ""
"All attacks strike an additional time. <style=cDeath>Lowered attack speed "
"and increased skill cooldowns</style>."
msgstr ""
"Всі атаки вдаряють ще один раз. <style=cDeath>Зменшує швидкість атаки та "
"збільшує час на перезаряджання здібностей</style>."

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFFORCE_LORE
msgid ""
"Ah, Youngling! You have returned once more, with what seems to be a full "
"bag, too! Full of scavengings, yes?\n"
"\n"
"Hmm. The pack is heavy, but it is nearly empty. You... You are not hiding "
"things from me, Youngling?\n"
"\n"
"...You found something very heavy. I see. Forgive me for my suspicions. Show "
"me this thing you have found.\n"
"\n"
"Ah! You are correct, Youngling. This thing is small, but difficult to hold. "
"It splinters and fragments, and each piece is just as heavy as the whole. "
"What a remarkable thing, this is!\n"
"\n"
"I will put it with the other wonderful things you have found. A thing like "
"this could be dangerous if it fell into the wrong hands. As for you, "
"Youngling... Hmm, I believe some repairs for your bag are in order. Come "
"with me."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFMASS_NAME
msgid "Relic of Mass"
msgstr "Реліквія маси"

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFMASS_DESC
msgid ""
"<style=cIsHealing>Increase maximum health</style> by <style=cIsHealing>{0}%</"
"style> <style=cStack>(+{0}% per stack)</style>. <style=cDeath>Reduce "
"acceleration and deceleration</style> by a factor of <style=cDeath>{1}</"
"style> <style=cStack>(+{1} per stack)</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFMASS_PICKUP
msgid ""
"Double your max health. <style=cDeath>Your movement has momentum</style>."
msgstr ""
"Подвоює ваше макс. здоров'я. <style=cDeath>Ви отримуєте інерцію у "
"пересуванні</style>."

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFMASS_LORE
msgid ""
"Ah, welcome back! Youngling, what have you found?\n"
"\n"
"Hmmm. More scavengings from the blasted heath? Very well. You may keep those "
"things, if you wish. Have you found anything else?\n"
"\n"
"Ah, you have? Let me see it then, youngling.\n"
"\n"
"Oh! This shape that you've found! It is stalwart, but not loyal. Powerful, "
"but yet also frail at the same time. It is a peculiar shape, to say the "
"least of it. Where did you find this, youngling?\n"
"\n"
"...You found it on the planet? Hmm. Worrisome. This was not created by those "
"sandfolk. Too complex, too powerful. Nor by those Lemurians. Tell me, "
"youngling, you did not steal this, did you?\n"
"\n"
"...You did not. I see. Very well. I would like to keep this shape. This "
"shape is dangerous if you do not understand it.\n"
"\n"
"Oh, my youngling, do not look so saddened. This shape is remarkable, and I "
"laud your work regardless of this. I simply want to keep it safe. Here, "
"perhaps a reward is in order. Come with me."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFTERMINATION_NAME
msgid "Relic of Termination"
msgstr "Реліквія термінування"

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFTERMINATION_DESC
msgid ""
"Every <style=cIsUtility>{0} seconds</style>, grants a buff which "
"<style=cIsDamage>marks</style> the next spawning enemy. If defeated within "
"<style=cIsUtility>30 seconds</style> <style=cStack>(-10% per stack)</style>, "
"they <style=cIsDamage>drop an item</style> <style=cStack>(item rarity scales "
"with stacks)</style>; if not, they drop <style=cIsDamage>nothing</style> and "
"delay the next mark. <style=cDeath>Marked enemies have significantly "
"increased stats</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFTERMINATION_PICKUP
msgid ""
"Every {0} seconds, mark an enemy and strengthen them. If defeated in time, "
"they drop an item; if not, they drop nothing."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFTERMINATION_LORE
msgid ""
"Youngling! Ah, I am so excited to see you return! Have you found anything "
"new?\n"
"\n"
"Oh? You have! Do show me, little one. There's no need to be shy.\n"
"\n"
"Hm... What have you found this time? It's sturdy and hollow, but when you "
"shake it... it sloshes, like an overripe nutapple. What a strange shape we "
"have here...\n"
"\n"
"Oh? Oh my. You were chased by a monster, you say... It did not follow you "
"here, correct?\n"
"\n"
"...It did not. But of course, it would be hard to find us here, wouldn't it, "
"Youngling?\n"
"\n"
"Here, I will take this away. Somewhere where it can bring no monsters to "
"us.\n"
"\n"
"...I understand. It is okay to be afraid sometimes, but you cannot let it "
"overwhelm you. Would it not be cruel to another wanderer to find this shape, "
"and suffer dearly for it?\n"
"\n"
"We will be safe here, Youngling. Come with me. You must be hungry after "
"being out for so long."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFTERMINATION_PREFIX
msgid "Terminal {0}"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFECHELON_NAME
msgid "Relic of Echelon"
msgstr "Реліквія ешелону"

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFECHELON_DESC
msgid ""
"Gain {1} (+{1} per stack) base damage and {2} (+{2} per stack) base health "
"for {3} seconds on use. Using an equipment ermanently increases its cooldown "
"by {0}%"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFECHELON_PICKUP
msgid ""
"Gain a massive buff on equipment use. <style=cDeath>Using an equipment "
"permanently increases its cooldown</style>."
msgstr ""
"Отримайте потужне підсилення від використання спорядження. "
"<style=cDeath>Використання спорядження назавжди збільшує час його "
"перезаряджання</style>."

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFECHELON_LORE
msgid ""
"No no Youngling, you are here too soon! I haven't the time to prepare. "
"Please...Come back later."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_PRIMAL_BIRTHRIGHT_NAME
msgid "Primal Birthright"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_PRIMAL_BIRTHRIGHT_DESC
msgid ""
"Grants <style=cIsUtility>{0}</style> <style=cStack>(+{1} per stack)</style> "
"Legendary Chest <style=cIsUtility>on each stage</style>, <style=cDeath>but "
"you cannot leave without claiming your birthright</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_PRIMAL_BIRTHRIGHT_PICKUP
msgid ""
"Grants a Legendary Chest on each stage, <style=cDeath>but you cannot leave "
"without claiming your birthright</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_PRIMAL_BIRTHRIGHT_LORE
msgid ""
"The symbols on the parchment are foreign to you. You do not understand what "
"they are, but somehow, you understand the meaning they carry. Power. Will. "
"Authority, and a message. \n"
"\n"
"\"The right to rule is earned through strength and wit, and those alone. It "
"cannot be granted by another. It cannot be granted by birth nor blood. Only "
"strength justifies itself.\"\n"
"You look back down. The flickering lights of the hull cast strange shapes in "
"the shard. Reflected shadows against its glow, coalescing into shapes that "
"coalesce into figures.\n"
"\n"
"Two shadows stumble aimlessly around in the reflection, against the backdrop "
"of dawn. Short, stubby shadows. A seed falls into one's hair, and it laughs "
"and plants it back into the soil. A seed falls into another's hands. It "
"gently pries the thing open, to learn what will grow.\n"
"\n"
"The shadows lengthen as the sun moves through the sky. Long, imposing "
"shadows against twilight. Positioned perfectly, like an eerie gate to the "
"light.\n"
"\n"
"One shadow begins to grow faster still, stretching until the whole world is "
"a blanket of darkness. The lone shadow thrashes against its prison, "
"indistinguishable against the sea of blackness, fiercely refusing to fade "
"away.\n"
"\n"
"One shadow remains in the light. It stands in front of the now rising sun, "
"eclipsing its light. Rays of golden sun wrap around it, forming a coronal "
"halo for the shadow. Standing out starkly against the world around it- "
"blinding, searing, formless. Selfish. It does not move.\n"
"\n"
"You squint your eyes, and the symbols hold a new meaning.\n"
"\n"
"\"It isn't fair.\""
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_ARMEDBACKPACK_NAME
msgid "Armed Backpack"
msgstr "Збройний рюкзак"

#: .strings.SS2_ITEM_ARMEDBACKPACK_DESC
msgid ""
"Chance on taking damage to fire a missile for <style=cIsDamage>{0}%</style> "
"<style=cStack>(+{0}% per stack)</style> base damage. Chance scales with "
