#: .strings.SS2_RUNSHROOM_BODY_NAME
msgid "Rushrum"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_UNLOCKABLE_LOG_RUNSHROOM
msgid "Logbook: Rushrum"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_RUNSHROOM_BODY_LORE
msgid ""
"We awoke in a panic, our tent ablaze. Our equipment a molten mass of the "
"periodic table.\n"
"\n"
"\"H-hey, over there! That thing!\"\n"
"\n"
"It was so small, it looked like it could be a bug under our shoe, yet the "
"mess it made... There was no other way.\n"
"\n"
"\"Stay here, I'm gonna go squeeze that thing to a fuckin' pulp.\"\n"
"\n"
"I sat there and watched as my crew lept like frogs at the small fungi, "
"unable to even graze its surface. Profanities like a siren in the air.\n"
"\n"
"Our efforts were fruitless. I signaled for the crew to return to aid in the "
"dowsing of the flames.\n"
"\n"
"\"Pipe down and get over here! The fire ain't dyin' by itself! The bastard's "
"like a roach, you won't catch it!\"\n"
"\n"
"The damages weren't covered."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MIMIC_BODY_NAME
#, fuzzy
msgid "Security Chest"
msgstr "Захисний дрон"

#: .strings.SS2_MIMIC_BODY_SUBTITLE
msgid "The Mimic"
msgstr "Мімік"

#: .strings.SS2_UNLOCKABLE_LOG_MIMIC
msgid "Logbook: Security Chest"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MIMIC_BODY_LORE
msgid ""
"\"Now, I'd like to see this as something of a learning experience, all "
"things considered. Evolutionary biology has a curious place for mimicry, my "
"friend- certain creatures seek not to be threatening or inviting by their "
"own merit, but rather by the means of seeming to be a different thing "
"entirely. Of course, evolution being random means that this isn't what we're "
"dealing with-\"\n"
"\n"
"\"It’s also not what we're dealing with because-\"\n"
"\n"
"\"No no, let me finish. In this case we have a very fascinating example, "
"don't we? A machine emulating another machine in such an animated way, as a "
"means to trick us into getting close- why, it's positively Wicklerian in "
"design, isn't it? Whoever made this thing really had a heart for it, don't "
"you think?\"\n"
"\n"
"\"...Dude, it just steals shit. Nothin' fancy about it.\"\n"
"\n"
"\"Nature really is beautiful, even in a place like this.\"\n"
"\n"
"\"Shut up and let’s keep moving. Ugh, god, why'd I have to get stuck with "
"this guy?\"\n"
"\n"
"-Signal echoes, UES Contact Light"
msgstr ""

