"\n"
"< ! > You can tap Ion Burst to fire a few shots, or hold it to fire them "
"all.\n"
"\n"
"< ! > Execution is a great crowd control AND single target tool. Don't "
"forget that its damage depends on how many targets it hits!\n"
"\n"
"< ! > If you find yourself getting swarmed, Crowd Dispersion can get enemies "
"off your back fast."
