#: .strings.SS2_EXECUTIONER_SWINGAXE_NAME
msgid "Ion Axe"
msgstr "Іонна сокира"

#: .strings.SS2_EXECUTIONER_SWINGAXE_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"Swing your axe for <style=cIsDamage>% damage</style>. <style=cIsUtility>Each "
"Secondary charge grants 4% maximum health in shield</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_EXECUTIONER_IONGUN_NAME
msgctxt ".strings.SS2_EXECUTIONER_IONGUN_NAME"
msgid "Ion Burst"
msgstr "Іонна черга"

#: .strings.SS2_EXECUTIONER_IONGUN_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"<style=cIsUtility>Recharging.</style> Fire a barrage of ionized bullets, "
"dealing <style=cIsDamage>{0}% damage</style> each. <style=cIsUtility>Up to 5 "
"charges are fired at a time</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_EXECUTIONER_IONBLAST_NAME
msgid "Ion Blast"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_EXECUTIONER_IONBLAST_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"Fire a blast of raw ion energy for <style=cIsDamage>% damage</style>. Can be "
"<style=cIsUtility>charged</style>, using multiple charges at once. "
"<style=cIsUtility>Restocks charges for every enemy you kill, depending on "
"strength</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_EXECUTIONER_DASH_NAME
msgctxt ".strings.SS2_EXECUTIONER_DASH_NAME"
msgid "Crowd Dispersion"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_EXECUTIONER_DASH_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"Boost forward and <style=cIsUtility>fear</style> all nearby enemies for "
"<style=cIsUtility>{0} seconds</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_EXECUTIONER_AXE_NAME
msgctxt ".strings.SS2_EXECUTIONER_AXE_NAME"
msgid "Execution"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_EXECUTIONER_AXE_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"<style=cIsUtility>Heavy</style>. <style=cIsDamage>Executing.</style> Launch "
"into the air and slam downwards with a massive ion axe for "
"<style=cIsDamage>{0}% damage</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_EXECUTIONER_AXESCEPTER_NAME
msgid "Crowd Execution"
msgstr "Страта натовпу"

#: .strings.SS2_EXECUTIONER_AXESCEPTER_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"Launch into the air and slam downward with your ion axe for "
"<style=cIsDamage>3000% damage</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_EXECUTIONER_ARMOR_NAME
msgid "Ion Juggernaut"
msgstr "Іонний джаґернаут"

#: .strings.SS2_EXECUTIONER_ARMOR_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"Equip a suit of ionized armor, giving <style=cIsUtility>60 armor</style> and "
"<style=cIsDamage>supercharging</style> your secondary skill for "
"<style=cIsDamage>4</style> seconds."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_EXECUTIONER_ARMORSCEPTER_NAME
msgid ""
"Equip a suit of ionized armor, giving <style=cIsUtility>80 armor</style> and "
"<style=cIsDamage>supercharging</style> your secondary skill for "
"<style=cIsDamage>4</style> seconds. Killing enemies <style=cIsUtility>fears</"
"style> nearby enemies for 4 seconds."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_KNIGHT_BODY_NAME
msgid "Knight"
msgstr "Лицар"

#: .strings.SS2_KNIGHT_BODY_SUBTITLE
msgid "Royal Guard"
msgstr "Королівський гвардієць"

#: .strings.SS2_KNIGHT_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"The Knight is a skilled expert in melee combat, dueling and parrying foes "
"with precise timing and execution.\n"
"\n"
"<color=#CCD3E0>< ! > parry."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_KNIGHT_OUTRO_FLAVOR
msgctxt ".strings.SS2_KNIGHT_OUTRO_FLAVOR"
msgid "..and so he left, battered to the core of hope."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_KNIGHT_OUTRO_FAILURE
msgctxt ".strings.SS2_KNIGHT_OUTRO_FAILURE"
msgid "..and so he vanished, shield shattered and hope snuffed out."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_KNIGHT_BODY_LORE
msgid "why are there knights in space"
msgstr "шо лицарі забули у космосі?"

#: .strings.SS2_KNIGHT_PASSIVE_NAME
msgctxt ".strings.SS2_KNIGHT_PASSIVE_NAME"
msgid "Invigorate"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_KNIGHT_PASSIVE_DESC
msgid ""
"A buff ward surronds you that grants allies in its radius "
"<style=cIsDamage>20% attack speed</style> and <style=cIsDamage>20% damage</"
"style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_KNIGHT_PRIMARY_SWORD_NAME
msgctxt ".strings.SS2_KNIGHT_PRIMARY_SWORD_NAME"
msgid "Aeonium Blade"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_KNIGHT_PRIMARY_SWORD_DESC
msgid ""
"Slice forward for <style=cIsDamage>200% damage</style>. Every third hit "
"stabs forward for <style=cIsDamage>400% damage</style>. While blocking, bash "
"enemies for <style=cIsDamage>400% damage</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_KNGIHT_PRIMARY_SWORD_UPRGADE_TOOLTIP
msgid ""
"<style=cKeywordName><color=#fa78f3>Empowered</color></style><style=cSub>Dash "
"forward, and strike for <style=cIsDamage>3x400% damage</style>.</style>"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_KEYWORD_PARRY
msgid ""
"<style=cKeywordName>Parry</style><style=cSub>Block an incoming hit to "
"<style=cIsUtility>stun</style> and deal <style=cIsDamage>350% damage</style> "
"to all enemies around you. You also become <style=cIsUtility>immune to "
"damage</style> for 1 second.</style>"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_KEYWORD_EMPOWERING
msgid ""
"<style=cKeywordName>Empowering</style><style=cSub><color=#fa78f3>Improves</"
"color> your next skill use.</style>"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_KNIGHT_SECONDARY_SHIELD_NAME
msgctxt ".strings.SS2_KNIGHT_SECONDARY_SHIELD_NAME"
msgid "Block"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_KNIGHT_SECONDARY_SHIELD_DESC
msgid ""
"Raise your shield, gaining <style=cIsUtility>400 armor</style>. Use before "
"an incoming strike to <style=cIsDamage>parry</style> it and "
"<color=#fa78f3>Empower</color> your next skill."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_KNIGHT_SECONDARY_SHIELD_DESC2
msgid ""
"Raise your shield, gaining <style=cIsUtility>400 armor</style> and replacing "
"your jump with a <style=cIsUtility>roll</style>. Use before an incoming "
"strike to <style=cIsDamage>parry</style> it and <color=#fa78f3>Empower</"
"color> your next skill."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_KNIGHT_SHIELD_BASH_NAME
msgctxt ".strings.SS2_KNIGHT_SHIELD_BASH_NAME"
msgid "Bash"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_KNIGHT_SHIELD_BASH_DESC
msgctxt ".strings.SS2_KNIGHT_SHIELD_BASH_DESC"
msgid ""
"Shield Bash in front of you for <style=cIsDamage>240% damage</style> and "
"<style=cIsUtility>stun</style> enemies hit."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_KNIGHT_UTILITY_LEAP_NAME
msgctxt ".strings.SS2_KNIGHT_UTILITY_LEAP_NAME"
msgid "Striking Rush"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_KNIGHT_UTILITY_LEAP_DESC
msgid ""
"Dash foward, spinning and slicing repeatedly for <style=cIsDamage>120% "
"damage</style> per hit. The number of hits scales with attack speed."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_KNIGHT_UTILITY_LEAP_UPGRADE_TOOLTIP
msgid ""
"<style=cKeywordName><color=#fa78f3>Empowered</color></"
"style><style=cSub>Travel further, dealing <style=cIsDamage>200% damage</"
"style> per hit.</style>"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_KNIGHT_SPECIAL_BANNER_NAME
msgctxt ".strings.SS2_KNIGHT_SPECIAL_BANNER_NAME"
msgid "Rally"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_KNIGHT_SPECIAL_BANNER_DESC
msgid ""
"Thrust a banner into the ground for <style=cIsDamage>750% damage</style>. "
"Nearby allies <style=cIsDamage>smite</style> enemies with their attacks, "
"reducing their armor and <style=cIsHealing>restoring health</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_KNIGHT_SPECIAL_BANNER_UPGRADE_TOOLTIP
msgid ""
"<style=cKeywordName><color=#fa78f3>Empowered</color></"
"style><style=cSub>Additionally grants <style=cIsUtility>X% barrier</style>.</"
"style>"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_NAME
msgid "MULE (SS2 BETA. VERY ROUGH PROTOTYPE)"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_SUBTITLE
msgid "Directive: Survive"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"Seriously this is a very rough early prototype of an old MULE design for "
"SS2. A full rework is planned, Enjoy it as a novelty, but its buggy."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_OUTRO_FLAVOR
msgid "..and so it left, engine sputtering, directive finally fulfilled."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_OUTRO_FAILURE
msgid "..and so it vanished, finally put out of commission."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_LORE
msgctxt ".strings.SS2_MULE_LORE"
msgid ""
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_KEYWORD_OVERCLOCKING
msgid ""
"<style=cKeywordName>Overclocking</style></style=cSub>Hold the button to "
"extend the skill's duration, but also extend the skill's cooldown length.</"
"sub>"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_KEYWORD_OVERCLOCKING2
msgid ""
"<style=cKeywordName>Overclocking</style></style=cSub>Hold the button to "
"charge the skill further, but also extend the skill's cooldown length.</sub>"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_PASSIVE_DRONE_NAME
msgid "Fail-Safe Assistance"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_PASSIVE_DRONE_DESC
msgid ""
"Taking damage to below <style=cIsHealth>25% health</style>activates your "
"personal <style=cIsHealing>Repair Drone</style>, healing for "
"<style=cIsHealing>50%</style> of your health. Has a <style=cIsUtility>60</"
"style> second cooldown."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_PUNCH_NAME
msgid "Interference Removal"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_PUNCH_DESC
msgid "Punch enemies for <style=cIsDamage>330% damage</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_KEYWORD_PUNCH_CALIBRATED
msgid ""
"<style=cKeywordName>Calibrated</style></style=cSub><style=cSub>Slam the "
"ground in front of you, dealing higher damage and sending out a shockwave. "
"(%s tbd)</style>"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_UPHEAVAL_NAME
msgid "Upheaval"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_UPHEAVAL_DESC
msgid ""
"<style=cIsDamage>Stunning</style>. Punch the ground in front of you, raising "
"a <style=cIsUtility>boulder</style> for <style=cIsDamage>450% damage</"
"style>. <style=cIsDamage>Boulders can be punched to be rolled.</style>"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_KEYWORD_UPHEAVAL_CALIBRATED
msgid ""
"<style=cKeywordName>Calibrated</style></style=cSub>Punch the ground in front "
"of you, raising up to 3 boulders at once."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_OLDPUNCH_NAME
msgid "Centrifugal Smash"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_OLDPUNCH_DESC
msgid ""
"<style=cIsUtility>Overclocking</style>. <style=cIsUtility>Stunning</style>. "
"Wind up, and throw a mighty punch forward for <style=cIsDamage>280% damage</"
"style>. <style=cIsDamage>Damage is multiplied by charge level, up to 4x</"
"style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_JUMP_NAME
msgid "Relocate"
msgstr "Релокація"

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_JUMP_DESC
msgid "<style=cIsUtility>Hold to charge</style> a powerful upwards leap."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_SPIN_NAME
msgctxt ".strings.SS2_MULE_SPIN_NAME"
msgid "Torque Calibration"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_SPIN_DESC
msgid ""
"<style=cIsUtility>Overclocking</style>. Rapidly spin, gradually increasing "
"<style=cIsUtility>movement speed</style> and <style=cIsUtility>increasing "
"armor</style> while dealing <style=cIsDamage>100% damage</style> per "
"rotation."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_NET_NAME
msgid "Immobilize"
msgstr "Знерухомлення"

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_NET_DESC
msgid ""
"Launch a <style=cIsUtility>net</style>, holding enemies within "
"<style=cIsUtility>12m</style> of impact in place and preventing them from "
"attacking for <style=cIsUtility>5</style> seconds. <style=cIsUtility>Flying "
"enemies are grounded</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_CHARGE_NAME
msgctxt ".strings.SS2_MULE_CHARGE_NAME"
msgid "Torque Calibration"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_CHARGE_DESC
msgid ""
"<style=cIsUtility>Calibrating</style>. <style=cIsUtility>Hold to charge up</"
"style>, and release to <style=cIsUtility>fling forward</style> whilst "
"spinning for <style=cIsDamage>(medium-high damage TBD)% damage</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_MULE_KEYWORD_CALIBRATING
msgid ""
"<style=cKeywordName>Calibrating</style><style=cSub>Can be canceled with "
"primary, secondary, or jump to perform more powerful \"calibrated\" variants "
"of those actions.</style>"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMBANDIT_NAME
msgid "Nemesis Bandit"
msgstr "Злостивий Бандит"

#: .strings.SS2_NEMBANDIT_SUBTITLE
msgid "Blackened Outlaw"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMBANDIT_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"The Nemesis Bandit carefully positions himself via camouflage technology to "
"wrangle foes and cull crowds. \n"
"\n"
"<color=#CCD3E0>< ! > Show no mercy."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMBANDIT_OUTRO_FLAVOR
msgid "..and so he left, with absolutely no regrets."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMBANDIT_OUTRO_FAILURE
msgid "..and so he returned, luck finally running out."
msgstr "...і він повернувся, його удача нарешті закінчилася."

#: .strings.SS2_NEMBANDIT_LORE
msgid "yehaw"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMBANDIT_PRIMARY_NAME
msgid "Gunslinger"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMBANDIT_PRIMARY_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"Fire a revolver shot for <style=cIsDamage>220% damage</style>. Can hold up "
"to 6 bullets."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMBANDIT_SECONDARY_NAME
msgid "Dynamite Toss"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMBANDIT_SECONDARY_DESCRIPTION
msgid "toss dynamite figure out #s later"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMBANDIT_SECONDARY_ALT_NAME
msgid "Coin Toss"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMBANDIT_SECONDARY_ALT_DESCRIPTION
msgid "you know what it does"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMBANDIT_SPECIAL_NAME
msgctxt ".strings.SS2_NEMBANDIT_SPECIAL_NAME"
msgid "Splatter"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMBANDIT_SPECIAL_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"Fire a shotgun burst for <style=cIsDamage>6x100% damage</style>. Kills "
"<style=cIsUtility>reset all your cooldowns.</style>"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_NAME
msgid "Nemesis Captain"
msgstr "Злостивий Капітан"

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_SUBTITLE
msgid "Down with the Ship"
msgstr "На дно з човном"

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"The Nemesis Captain issues orders to control the battlefield and fight "
"safely from behind his Adaptive Microbots.\n"
"\n"
"<color=#CCD3E0>< ! > Keep your cool. Using Orders too quickly will build "
"Stress, leaving you vulnerable."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_OUTRO_FLAVOR
msgid "..and so he left, lighting up a fresh smoke."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_OUTRO_FAILURE
msgid "..and so he vanished, retired at last."
msgstr "...і він був стертий, нарешті у відставці."

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_LORE
msgid "This planet sucks man.. *takes hit from cigar*"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_STRESSPASSIVE_NAME
msgid "idk what to call half of this stuff or how to present it to the player"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_STRESSPASSIVE_DESC
msgid ""
"Gain <style=cIsHealth>Stress</style> while in danger. When Stress reaches "
"maximum, temporarily become <style=cIsHealth>Overstressed</style>, reducing "
"<style=cIsUtility>movement speed</style>, <style=cIsUtility>armor</style>, "
"and <style=cIsDamage>damage</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_KEYWORD_STRESS
msgid ""
"<style=cKeywordName>Stress</style><style=cSub>Gain Stress by being "
"surrounded by enemies, receiving damage, or using Orders. Reduce Stress by "
"dealing Critical Strikes, healing, killing enemies, using certain Orders, "
"and being out of combat."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_KEYWORD_OVERSTRESS
msgid ""
"<style=cKeywordName>Overstress</style><style=cSub>Become subjected to the "
"effects of maximum Stress, as well as -30% movement speed, -20 armor, and "
"-50% damage until the Stress meter counts down to 0."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_PRIMARY_NAME
msgid "Standard Issue"
msgstr "Стандартне видання"

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_PRIMARY_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"Rapidly fire for <style=cIsDamage>90% damage</style> per bullet. Can hold up "
"to 20 bullets."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_SECONDARY_NAME
msgid "Personal Backup"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_SECONDARY_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"<style=cIsDamage>Stunning</style>. Arm your cane rifle, then fire a shot for "
"<style=cIsDamage>680% damage</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_PUNCH_NAME
msgid "fujin"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_PUNCH_DESCRIPTION
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<style=cIsDamage>Stunning</style>. Throw a punch in front for "
"<style=cIsDamage>150% damage</style>."
msgstr ""
"Випускає електричну дугу, що завдає <style=cIsDamage>{0}% шкоди</style>."

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_HAIDARA_NAME
msgid "raijin"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_HAIDARA_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"<style=cIsDamage>Shocking</style>. Discharge a thunderbolt in front for "
"<style=cIsDamage>440% damage</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERS_NAME
msgid "Adaptive Microbots"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERS_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"Deploy 1 of 4 <style=cIsUtility>Microbot Orders</style>. Using Orders "
"increases <style=cIsHealth>Stress</style>. <style=cIsUtility>Hold the key</"
"style> of an Order to <style=cIsUtility>discard</style> it."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERNULL_NAME
msgid "Refresh Order"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERNULL_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"Devise a new plan of attack, slightly increasing <style=cIsHealth>Stress</"
"style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERSTRIKE_NAME
msgid "ORDER: Strike"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERSTRIKE_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"<style=cIsUtility>Stunning</style>. Aim a Microbot and fire a laser, "
"<style=cIsDamage>exploding</style> for <style=cIsDamage>1400% damage</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERSTRIKETRIPLE_NAME
msgid "ORDER: Strike 3x"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERSTRIKETRIPLE_DESCRIPTION
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<style=cIsUtility>Stunning</style>. Aim a Microbot and fire a laser, "
"<style=cIsDamage>exploding</style> for <style=cIsDamage>600% damage</style>. "
"<style=cIsUtility>Can be fired 3 times.</style>"
msgstr ""
"<style=cIsDamage>{0}%</style> шанс <style=cIsDamage>отруїти</style> ворога, "
"періодично завдаючи <style=cIsDamage>{1}%</style> <style=cStack>(+{1}% за "
"кожен дублікат)</style> базової шкоди."

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERSTRIKEFROST_NAME
msgid "ORDER: Strike PSI"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERSTRIKEFROST_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"<style=cIsUtility>Freezing</style>. Aim a Microbot and fire a laser, "
"<style=cIsDamage>exploding</style> for <style=cIsDamage>1100% damage</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERSTRIKESHOCK_NAME
msgid "ORDER: Strike KOPPA"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERSTRIKESHOCK_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"<style=cIsUtility>Shocking</style>. Aim a Microbot and fire a laser, "
"<style=cIsDamage>exploding</style> for <style=cIsDamage>900% damage</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERREGEN_NAME
msgid "ORDER: Administer Relaxant"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERREGEN_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"Temporarily increase the rate at which Stress decreases for "
"<style=cIsUtility>15 seconds</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERREDUCE_NAME
msgid "ORDER: Administer Stimulant"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERREDUCE_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"Temporarly decrease the amount of Stress gained from all sources by "
"<style=cIsUtility>50%</style> for <style=cIsUtility>10 seconds.</style>"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERRECOVER_NAME
msgid "ORDER: Total Reset"
msgstr "НАКАЗ: Повне скидання"

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERRECOVER_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"Massively decrease your current amount of stress, while also "
"<style=cIsUtility>discarding all other Orders</style>. Stress removed is "
"increased per Order lost."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERHEAL_NAME
msgid "ORDER: Invigoration Field"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERHEAL_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"<style=cIsHealing>Heal</style> nearby allies for </style>6%</style> of their "
"<style=cIsHealth>maximum health</style> every second, and also grant "
"<style=cIsUtility>50 armor</style> and <style=cIsDamage>+20% attack speed</"
"style> for <style=cIsUtility>12 seconds</style."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERGRAVITY_NAME
msgid "ORDER: Gravity Well"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERGRAVITY_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"<style=cIsUtility>Pull</syle> nearby enemies for <style=cIsUtility>8 "
"seconds</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_NAME
msgctxt ".strings.SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_NAME"
msgid "Nemesis Commando"
msgstr "Злостивий Командос"

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_SUBTITLE
msgctxt ".strings.SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_SUBTITLE"
msgid "Lone Echo"
msgstr "Самотнє відлуння"

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"The Nemesis Commando is a wildcard on the battlefield, capable of turning "
"any situation to his favor.\n"
"\n"
"<color=#CCD3E0>< ! > Single Tap can be used to deal with foes at any "
"distance. Combine it with Blade of Cessation up close to shred foes.\n"
"\n"
"< ! > Gouge is a powerful debuff that can critical hit and activate item "
"effects, on top of its heavy damage.\n"
"\n"
"< ! > Proper balance of melee and ranged combat is key, and Tactical Roll "
"grants high armor to help enter and exit battles.\n"
"\n"
"< ! > Disrupt enemies with Submission, whether it be to aid in an escape or "
"get the jump on an unsuspecting target."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_OUTRO_FLAVOR
msgctxt ".strings.SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_OUTRO_FLAVOR"
msgid "..and so he left, newfound sense of humanity within."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_OUTRO_FAILURE
msgid "..and so he vanished, humanity lost without a trace."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_LORE
msgid ""
"He lays to rest by a fire, setting the weapons he carries within an arm's "
"reach. Checking his surroundings, hoping the cave he hid in would be enough "
"shelter. Some would say it is not wise to be overly cautious. He would say, "
"<link=\"textShaky\">they have not seen enough</link>.\n"
"\n"
"The service pistol he got when he enlisted. Well used, dirtied, and loved. "
"It's brought him through thick and thin, no matter the circumstance. Some "
"would say that only a fool would trust their weapon. He would say, "
"<link=\"textShaky\">your weapon is all you can trust.</link>\n"
"\n"
"The blade of a fallen brother of war. Picked from what he could scavenge of "
"the last of humanity he's seen. Some would say it keeps their spirits "
"united. He would say, <link=\"textShaky\">it keeps their spirits from "
"joining for as long as possible.</link>\n"
"\n"
"The loads of cargo that landed with him. Each item picked from a chest, "
"keeping him alive in one way or another. Dozens of shipments to anyone but "
"him. Some would say they aren't his to take. He would say, "
"<link=\"textShaky\">if he doesn't take them, then no one else will</link>.\n"
"\n"
"The glow of a violet light coming from deeper within the cave. Calming, "
"warming... beckoning. Welcoming him deeper and deeper, promising safety. "
"Some would say that what sounds too good to be true usually is. He would "
"say, <link=\"textWavy\">Faust was a wise man</link>."
msgstr ""

